WEBVTT

00:02:58.392 --> 00:03:01.587
This is generosity and humanity

00:03:01.587 --> 00:03:05.961
that is remarkable.

00:03:05.961 --> 00:03:08.955
Think about it this way, proportionately.

00:03:08.955 --> 00:03:10.711
It would be as if

00:03:10.711 --> 00:03:13.702
the entire population of Germany,

00:03:13.702 --> 00:03:15.567
80 million people,

00:03:15.567 --> 00:03:20.957
would flee to the United States in just three years.

00:03:20.957 --> 00:03:24.118
Half of the entire population of Syria

00:03:24.118 --> 00:03:26.548
is now uprooted,

00:03:26.548 --> 00:03:28.303
most of them inside the country.

00:03:28.303 --> 00:03:30.598
Six and a half million people